Interface TriFunction<I1,I2,I3,O>

Type Parameters:
I1 - the type of the first input argument
I2 - the type of the second input argument
I3 - the type of the third input argument
O - the type of the result of the
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface TriFunction<I1,I2,I3,O>
A function that accepts two arguments and produces a result.
